# Database — ignore all DBs EXCEPT the two snapshots we intentionally ship to
# the HF Space. The Hub applies .gitignore server-side, so without these
# negations the uploaded .db files are silently dropped from the commit.
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.csv
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

